{
  "stem": "2316.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So-- and all the-- we had two temples and they were both Orthodox.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we observed all the rules and regulations as far as [NON-ENGLISH] was concerned.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I went to [NON-ENGLISH] besides going to regular school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my brothers went to-- also to [NON-ENGLISH] and plus school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had a private tutor come in the house, teach us Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We spoke fluently Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We started lessons in Hebrew when we were like four years old, all of us, all three kids.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They gave us a pretty good education for youngsters as long as possible until the war started.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The best part, of course, that I loved, were-- were when all the families, you know, would be together and visit and go to the park on Shabbos afternoon and singing the Shabbos songs.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I don't know, there was some kind of like-- the house used to light up when it came like Friday night before Shabbos.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Everybody would be bathed and dressed, and lights were on, and the candles were shining, and-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was such an enjoyable time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I wish I could enjoy it now as much, but I can't.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It just can't be the same.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I miss it terribly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And especially the family, the visitation, and-- and being together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It's just such a unity.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It's very difficult to explain.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And some people really struggled and they were poorer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But there's tons and tons of love and caring.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the children were so loved, and the mothers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And there was much respect and [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was a lot of strictness, also.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like my father would always say, you know-- if I would say, Dad, what would you do if I'd go out with a Gentile boy?",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
